column10: Lakefront all impact glass home in the resort community of PGA Verano. Enjoy stunning sunsets over the shimmering wide lake while relaxing by the pool. This home is within walking distance to the pools, clubhouse, fitness center and tennis courts. Also seconds away from the golf cart path into the three championship PGA golf courses. This home has an upgraded kitchen with built in wall oven and undermount cabinet lighting. Owner has added custom window treatments and mirrored wall in the great room. The great room also has a built in wine bar and there is molding in the formal dining room. Verano is a resort style community with so much to do! Meet new people, exercise, take up a craft, it's all here in Verano. THE PGA VERANO CLUB TALAVERA & LIFESTYLE:PGA Verano is a unique community with all-inclusive resort amenities. Verano has a golf cart path for PGA Golf Members minutes to the Clubhouse & 3 PGA golf courses (membership is not required). Included with your HOA fee is a state-of-the-art fitness center, aerobics studio, locker rooms with massage and sauna. An indoor heated JR Olympic pool and spa, an outdoor heated resort beach edge pool with spa and covered lounge area. Included for your pleasure are five har tru tennis courts, 2 bocce courts, a basketball court, 27 pickle ball courts w/ small clubhouse, tot lot and two very luxurious dog parks. This community has a full-time social events and fitness coordinator with a very welcoming community of residents. Verano has a full calendar of events from museum trips to water volleyball. In addition to our fitness & aquatics pavilion we have a 19, 000-sq. ft. social club called Club Talavera. The social club offers a piano bar lounge, craft room, card room, demonstration cooking kitchen, stage and banquet room, and a grand hall with fireplace. In the rear you'll find a concert lawn, covered patio with outside fireplace, and a fire pit down by the lake. This all connects to the heated outdoor resort pool with private cabanas. The new Publix supermarket is right outside the gate via golf cart, bike or walk away. Cleveland Clinic / Martin Memorial Health System facility is just minutes away off the Traditions exit. PGA Verano is a golf cart friendly community.PICKEL BALL:27 PICKLE BALL COURT FACILITY lighted courtsTENNIS: Verano currently has five tennis courts for team play. We now have Men's and Ladies tennis teams playing in area matches with team practices and a coach. column10: Welcome Home! This single family home will not last long! A great place to call home! Concrete block construction. Built in 2014 with newer construction codes and better insurance rates. Light and Bright. Great room floor plan with a breakfast bar and breakfast nook in the kitchen. Sliding glass doors lead you out to the fenced backyard. Split floor plan. 3 bedroom, 2 bath with an inside laundry room. Deep and tall 2 car garage with an accessible crawl space for additional storage use! So much potential for the next owner! Located on the dividing line of Dunedin and Clearwater. This property falls in the city of Dunedin/incorporated Pinellas County. Public water and Septic here. A short ride to Downtown Dunedin where you will find all sorts of incredible small businesses that are OPEN and thriving the Pandemic! Restaurants, bars, breweries, boutique shops, ice cream shops, clothing stores, grocer, wine shops, museums and so much more! The Pinellas Exercise Trail also runs through the downtown area. The Dunedin Fishing Pier is also OPEN to the public. The City of Dunedin Bagpipers are there to entertain you during the breathtaking sunsets on most Fri. and Sat. evenings. A real sense of old fashioned community fun & excitement! Come and live the lifestyle you desire in the OPEN state of sunny Florida! Close to public transit, Countryside Mall, grocery stores and the best beaches Pinellas County has to offer.

Do not miss your opportunity to own this home!

column2: 11081 SW Visconti Way, Port Saint Lucie, FL, 34986
column10: You can't help smile when you walk into this move in ready coastal decorated home. Well priced, making this home perfect for a full time home, rental or winter getaway. This all impact glass home with tile floors throughout has a private and quiet location. It is also well positioned to all of Verano's fabulous amenities. The owners have added undermount lighting and moldings to the kitchen cabinets as well as granite countertops & stainless steel appliances. Both bathrooms showers have tile to the ceiling and lovely upgraded lighting. You'll enjoy many hours entertaining out in your screened patio with great eastern exposure.Please note both wine coolers in the den and freezer in the garage do not convey with the property. Furniture and artwork negotiable THE PGA VERANO CLUB TALAVERA & LIFESTYLE:PGA Verano is a unique community with all-inclusive resort amenities. Verano has a golf cart path for PGA Golf Members minutes to the Clubhouse & 3 PGA golf courses (membership is not required). Included with your HOA fee is a state-of-the-art fitness center, aerobics studio, locker rooms with massage and sauna. An indoor heated JR Olympic pool and spa, an outdoor heated resort beach edge pool with spa and covered lounge area. Included for your pleasure are five har tru tennis courts, 2 bocce courts, a basketball court, 27 pickle ball courts w/ small clubhouse, tot lot and two very luxurious dog parks. This community has a full-time social events and fitness coordinator with a very welcoming community of residents. Verano has a full calendar of events from museum trips to water volleyball. In addition to our fitness & aquatics pavilion we have a 19, 000-sq. ft. social club called Club Talavera. The social club offers a piano bar lounge, craft room, card room, demonstration cooking kitchen, stage and banquet room, and a grand hall with fireplace. In the rear you'll find a concert lawn, covered patio with outside fireplace, and a fire pit down by the lake. This all connects to the heated outdoor resort pool with private cabanas. The new Publix supermarket is right outside the gate via golf cart, bike or walk away. Cleveland Clinic / Martin Memorial Health System facility is just minutes away off the Traditions exit. PGA Verano is a golf cart friendly community.PICKEL BALL:27 PICKLE BALL COURT FACILITY with some lighted courtsTENNIS: Verano currently has five tennis courts for team play. We now have Men's and Ladies tennis teams playing in area matches with team practices and a coach. GOLF: Verano is minutes from the golf cart path (for PGA Golf Members only) to the 3-championship public/private golf courses. Public play is available (check availability with the PGA) or pick from a variety of private memberships. Located within PGA Village is also the Legacy private golf and tennis club. You are not required to join any golf clubs to live in Verano.DINNING & SHOPPING:Residents of Verano enjoy the public Taplow Pub, PGA's newly renovated pub that serves breakfast, lunch and dinner. It's just a quick golf cart or car trip around the bend. Reasonably social members are also available. Which offer use of the PGA Golf Clubhouse and dining. Saint Lucie West offers a variety of other dining options as well. The Traditions shopping area is just down the road offering the popular big box, restaurants and boutique stores.CROSSTOWN PARKWAY EXIT 120 allows residents to easily access US 1. BEACHES AND PARKS: You'll enjoy many lovely local area beaches and parks here. Verano is about 25 minutes to the nearest beach. Information is believed to be correct but not warranted, personality verify all information before relying on said information.MEDICAL:Martin Memorial Health Systems is now a part of the Cleveland Clinic. This facility is minutes away from PGA VeranoInformation is believed to be correct but not warranted, personality verify all information before relying on said information.

column10: SHOWCASE HOME~ MAKE YOUR MOVE! Taylor Morrison Lazio built in Feb of 2019 appointed on an oversized private lot in the gated enclave of Esplanade at Starkey Ranch shows like a model with luxurious touches! Immaculate 3BR + office, 3BA, 2 CAR tandem garage home nestled on an oversized lot with no rear neighbors adorned with all the upgrades you want and a maintenance-free lifestyle rich with amenities! In this one-story MASTERPIECE of a home, the curb appeal is evident with the popular Mediterranean inspired Elevation A, tile roof, sealed paver driveway, attractive landscaping & walkway lead to a stylish beveled glass inlay front door. The OPEN FLOOR PLAN unfolds as you enter the foyer highlighted by double tray ceiling with crown molding. Upgraded 8ft doors throughout. No carpet here! All living areas, including the kitchen have an upgraded, warm wood-look tile flooring which compliments the neutral walls. All bedrooms feature engineered hardwood. This open floor plan is perfect for entertaining! The generous sized living room is saturated in natural light, overlooks the private screened lanai and is complimented by extras like crown molding. A formal dining room space is adjacent. This home has the DREAM KITCHEN you have been looking for! Custom upgraded Level 5 Antique Vanilla Wood Cabinets are complimented by oil rubbed bronze hardware, stunning gold & cream toned quartz countertops, under cabinet lighting & diamond stone backsplash. The extended center island features bar sink, breakfast bar with space for 4 barstools and additional cabinet storage. GE Monogram Stainless steel appliances include Refrigerator, 5 burner gas cooktop enhanced by custom hood, dishwasher and built-in oven & microwave. Large closet Pantry with upgraded built ins. The spacious master suite has 4 tall windows, tray with crown molding & ceiling fan. Escape to your luxurious master ensuite featuring upgraded dual sinks with quartz counters, makeup area, extra cabinet & drawer space, Oversized Frameless glass enclosed walk-in shower with rain head shower, upgraded tile & decorative niche. An incredibly spacious walk-in master closet has high end built-ins helping you stay organized with clothes & linens. Featured in this SPLIT FLOOR PLAN is the office with French doors. The second generous sized bedroom has a ceiling fan, walk in closet and ensuite bath with walk in shower. Guest bath features granite single sink, tub/shower combo with listello accent and tile floors. 3rd bedroom is located at the front of the home. Large Laundry room offers rough in for utility sink & newer washer/dryer included! 3 car tandem garage upgraded with epoxy floors plus built in storage rack! The backyard oasis is home to the extended screened lanai with no rear neighbors! A top of the line outdoor kitchen offers 5 burner gas grill, sink, refrigerator complimented by stone accent, hexagonal backsplash & seating at granite bar is the perfect place to relax or entertain guests and watch football! There is plenty of space to add a pool. Home is situated close to front of Esplanade. Resort style living in Esplanade includes resort styler heated pool, 24-hour fitness center, firepit, 6, 000 sqft clubhouse, tennis & pickleball courts, secure gated entry, lawn & pest care, dog park, lifestyle director and so much more! If you want affordable luxury, this is a must see!!

Located in the gorgeous and highly sought after Eagles GATED GOLFING community, with 2 Championship golf courses and Schools nearby. A RARE find at this price level. The spacious master bedroom enjoys VIEWS over the pool and conservation area beyond. In the master bath you will find a large WALK-IN CLOSET SHOWER GARDEN TUB HIS & HERS DUAL SINKS TILE FLOORING. The master bedroom is split from the further two bedrooms and bathroom. The indoor laundry room with additional storage is conveniently located close to the kitchen. Enjoy sitting by the private SCREENED IN pool with views over the conservation area beyond. The pool was previously heated by solar panels, which were removed when the roof was placed but all pipework still remains. column10: Amazing custom pool home on a CONSERVATION lot in much desired BRIGHTON PARK. Privacy abounds with a tranquil setting overlooking Mother Nature and all she has to offer. This fine home offers the sought-after THREE WAY SPLIT floor plan. GRANITE countertops throughout and an attractive WOOD-BURNING FIREPLACE in the family room. The master bedroom is light and bright and provides access to the pool and a delightful wooded view. The combination living and dining room can be found in the front of the home. The spacious kitchen will bring out the chef in you allowing you to spread out with an abundance of GRANITE COUNTERS, several 42-inch maple cabinets provide a place to store everything.   The vaulted ceilings bring in the light and tray ceilings add a nice designer touch.   The additional bedrooms are oversized with one having an adjoining bath, that serves as the pool bath too. The side of the home has been gated providing more space to spread out - plant a garden or make a dog run?  Carillion offers many fine features including tot lots, ball field, tennis courts, and volleyball. Zoned for FINE SEMINOLE COUNTY SCHOOLS (two within walking distance of this home). Conveniently located near local employers - Lockheed Martin, Siemens, Research Park and close by access the 417 expressway. Home warranty included for your peace of mind. Come see this fine home before it's gone. It won't last long!

column10: Carefree living at its best. Gated resort style community with beautiful pond views. Immaculate townhome that offers 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, 1, 962 square feet of living space and a spacious 2 car attached garage. An open concept floor plan is expressed with soaring ceilings and lots of windows for sunshine. The kitchen is a chefs delight with granite counter tops, stainless appliances, glass cook-top range, walk-in pantry recessed lights and large center island with snack bar. The dining area has plenty of space for entertaining and has an easy flow into the living room with vaulted ceiling and glass sliding doors that lead out to the screened patio. Main level master bedroom has plenty of room for extensive furniture, ceiling fan and a private ensuite. The master bath has a large double sink granite bath, walk-in master closet and a glass enclosed shower. The additional bath also has a large double sink vanity and tile floors. Second level loft space that's perfect for a movie room or family games area and overlooks downstairs living room. Enjoy your morning coffee in the private screened patio with brick paved floors and plenty of seating area. Feel like you're on vacation every day at the resort style pool with scenic pond views, playground, lounging area and dog park. Quiet neighborhood and convenient to schools, shopping and great restaurants. Easy access to I-75 and Crosstown Expressway.

column10: View the home virtually with this link: my.matterport.com/show/?m=inxcHhhsqBf&mls=1 Have you been searching for the PERFECT home to check all your boxes? Look no further... you have FOUND IT! Stunning, David Weekley Aronwood floorplan with upgrades galore! This wonderful family home is nestled in the gated community of Brooker Reserve that is just minutes to some of the county's best schools and tons of shopping and dining! From the moment you set your eyes on this home you will know you have found the ONE! Meticulous landscaping, striking elevation and a charming entryway all welcome you into the grand design! NO detail has been overlooked in this home... from the staggered tile flooring to the elegant crown molding, this one is a WINNER! The oversized dining room behind double French doors will be your favorite place to entertain! The absolute STAR of the home is the spectacular kitchen! Granite counters, designer cabinets, tile backsplash, stainless appliances and w huge pantry! Open to the kitchen is a more casual eat-in nook space! The open great room will be your families favorite place to kick back and relax! With an accent tray ceiling and walls of windows letting the natural light flood the space effortlessly! One of the very BEST features of this home is the versatile 3-way split floor plan! The master retreat is secluded at the back of the house with more decorative tray ceiling with crown molding and a lovely en-suite with a relaxing soaking tub, separate shower, his and her sinks and walk-in closet! Two more bedrooms are tucked away at the front of the house along with a full bathroom and the 4th bedroom doubles as a Jr. master suite with it's very own en-suite bathroom! Great for an in-law suite or college kid retreat! Need even more space for the family? Head upstairs to the ENORMOUS bonus room! Complete with a closet and full bath, this is an essential space that could easily be transformed into a home office, media room or even a homeschooling space! We promise there isn't another home like this one on the market! Don't miss your opportunity, schedule a private tour today!

column10: BACK ON MARKET!! CLICK ON VIRTUAL TOUR....YOU WILL LOVE THIS HOME!!! Gorgeous 4BD/2.5 BA Pool Home with side entry garage and Game/Media Room in highly desirable Brentwood Hills with all the amenities! Stroke your ego with one of the largest homes in the neighborhood. This Joe Bricketto Touch of Glass classic that boasts over 3400 SF with signature Terracotta Roof surely won't disappoint and is Freshly Painted Inside and Out!! As you enter, the high ceilings welcome you and immediately you know that you are home. This one owner home has a separate formal living and dining room which offer great space for entertainment that lead you into the updated kitchen that comes complete with updated appliances including brand new built-in microwave, granite countertop w/ breakfast bar, granite backsplash, 42 inch staggered cabinets, double ovens, electric cooktop, and large drawers for easy storage. The eat-in kitchen leads out to the patio with sliding glass doors and has a complete view of the backyard. The BRAND NEW Vinyl floors are contiguous through the downstairs level and lead you to the open family room with pocket sliding doors that completely open to the patio and backyard. The master bedroom is located on the first floor and offers enough space for a seating area and has his and her walk-in closets. The master bath also has his and her sinks and has a jetted garden tub, separate walk-in shower and separate water closet. There is also a Mirrored TV on the wall perfect for catching the news or your favorite show while getting ready. The stairs include newly installed carpet and lead you to the other 3 bedrooms located on the 2nd floor. The rooms are extremely large for secondary bedrooms and one of the rooms offers double closets! Don't forget the Bonus room!!! It comes complete with a screen projector and screen, FIVE LUSH Theater chairs perfect for viewing new movies that are released on demand AND a pool table that will remain!!! You just can't find a house like this in the area in such great condition and with these updates! One of the AC units was replaced within the last year and brand new ceiling fans have been installed on the patio, in family room and one of the bedrooms. But wait, there is more!! The pool in the back boasts an inground spa with heating available, there is a covered patio and plenty of yard space, all of which is completely fenced! And the extended driveway, allows for plenty of vehicles! Let's not forget the perfect location. The property is situated in Brentwood Hills which offers a mutli-purpose field, a clubhouse, pool, tennis courts, and playground. The home is also minutes from major shopping and dining, Brandon Town Center, great access to the Selmon and I-75, MacDill AFB, and about 40 minutes from the airport and is in a great school district. If you were looking for a gem....you've found it.

column2: 806 E Windward Way Apt 514, Lantana, FL, 33462
column10: If you've ever dreamed of living in a resort, here is your opportunity! RARELY AVAILABLE 5th floor CORNER condo in the #806 Tower, the only Moorings building located directly on the waterfront. Fabulous sunrise, Intracoastal, Marina & pool views from the oversized balcony! This isn't your typical cookie cutter condo floorplan, it's a wide u-shaped layout. Expansive open concept living room & dining room, kitchen with Giallo Veneziano granite, breakfast bar, stainless & black appliances. Split bedroom floorplan, with 2 oversized master suites, each with its own bathroom and large walk-in closet. Laundry with full size washer & dryer inside the unit. Hurricane IMPACT GLASS windows & sliding door. 1 assigned parking space in the garage. Private storage locker directly across from the unit. Bicycle rack in garage. Building insurance, exterior maintenance, water, basic cable and internet are all included in the monthly fee. Just pay electric. The Moorings offers amenities you'd find at a vacation destination: clubhouse, resort pool, hot tub, fitness center, Cheese & Wine Cafe, conference room, dry saunas, on-site management, free valet and 24/7 security patrols. Pets (for owners) are welcome...1 pet max weight of 35 lbs, or 2 pets with a combined weight of 50 lbs. Investors, immediate rentals are allowed, with a 30 day minimum stay required, up to 12x per year. Suntex Marina is on-site, for dock availability. Close to lots of great dining options, like Old Key Lime House, Johnny G's & Dune Deck Cafe. Lyman Kayak Park, Lantana Bicentennial Park and Playground are just down the street. Only 1.5 miles to the beach! 15 minutes to Palm Beach International Airport. Quick on/off I95. Data & measurements are deemed reliable but subject to errors, omissions and changes.

column10: Fabulous, panoramic views of the beautiful wide- water Intracoastal, Singer Island skyline & ocean horizon from this appealing 21st floor Condo. East exposure with lovely sunrises and lots of natural light. Million dollar views throughout this wonderful residence in impeccable condition. PET FRIENDLY, 2 pets permitted, max. 35 pounds each. Marina Grande is a secluded, gated, high-rise community located immediately adjacent to the Intracoastal - the gateway to Singer Island. This generously sized 2BDR/2BTH Condo PLUS an additional den/office provides more than 1800sf, plus a balcony with magnificent views. Open Euro kitchen with attractive granite, cherry wood cabinets, SS appliances, floor to ceiling hurricane impact sliding glass doors and windows offer marvelous water-views. Marina Grande's first class, resort-style amenities provide a luxurious lifestyle to its resident. The amenities are located on the 7th floor recreation deck perched over-looking the Intracoastal, Peanut Island and the Palm Beach Inlet and include: a heated lap swimming pool, waterfront clubhouse, tennis courts, sunning deck with two hot tubs, kids wading pool, newly updated summer kitchen pavilions with grills and dining areas, sauna & steam rooms, billiards and card rooms, social salon with catering kitchen and bar. A wide array of activities and entertainment are offered. Covered garage parking and free valet parking. Additional AC storage locker. Buildings are pre-wired with cable, high speed internet and telephone. ATTN BOATERS: Full service SunTex Marina onsite with dry dock storage for up to 50' boats, convenient day docks, plus instant access to the PB Inlet and popular water-front venues, it s a perfect match for the boater and salt-life lovers alike!

column10: Don't miss out on this luxurious Homes by West Bay Cypress model in Tampa Bays #1 master planned community of Starkey Ranch!This meticulously maintained Mediterranean style home is on an oversized corner lot with tile roofing, 2 car garage and WALKING DISTANCE to Homestead Park and Pool! This house has been extensively upgraded and is move in ready. As you enter this beautiful home through the majestic 3/4 full light front door with sidelights on each side, you see the showpiece stair case to the left and to the right an elegant dining room that can be used as a den or study. As you pass the dining room, you enter the spacious great room, gourmet kitchen and brunch area. The gourmet kitchen has upgraded stainless steel appliances including a wall oven and microwave, a 36' five burner natural gas cooktop!The upgraded espresso 42' cabinets with crown molding and dovetail kitchen drawers with cushion close are complimented by beautiful quartz countertops with a large island, backsplash and an oversized kitchen sink. The perfectly located pantry is easy to access and makes this kitchen a cooks dream. The downstairs and upstairs bathrooms and laundry room has upgraded ceramic tile, additional canned lighting throughout the home and the great room and bonus room are prewired for surround sound speakers. Upstairs you'll find even more upgrades that will make this beautiful home even more attractive. The oversized master bedroom with double entry doors and sitting area is an owners dream. The master bathroom and secondary bathroom both have upgraded white cabinets and beautiful counters to match. Off of the master bathroom is your oversized walk in closet that has, more than enough room for the both of you. The extra wide hallway leads you past three amazing bedrooms and into a large bonus room that is large enough to accommodate all activities. Homestead Park is only a couple steps away where you will find a community pool, playground, dog park and BBQ area. If you are looking for a model condition and move in ready home then look no more! Contact me today for your VIP showing or virtual tour.

column10: Don't miss out on this luxurious Homes by West Bay Cypress model in Tampa Bays #1 master planned community of Starkey Ranch!This meticulously maintained Mediterranean style home is on an oversized corner lot with tile roofing, 2 car garage and WALKING DISTANCE to Homestead Park and Pool! This house has been extensively upgraded and is move in ready. As you enter this beautiful home through the majestic 3/4 full light front door with sidelights on each side, you see the showpiece stair case to the left and to the right an elegant dining room that can be used as a den or study. As you pass the dining room, you enter the spacious great room, gourmet kitchen and brunch area. The gourmet kitchen has upgraded stainless steel appliances including a wall oven and microwave, a 36' five burner natural gas cooktop!The upgraded espresso 42' cabinets with crown molding and dovetail kitchen drawers with cushion close are complimented by beautiful quartz countertops with a large island, backsplash and an oversized kitchen sink. The perfectly located pantry is easy to access and makes this kitchen a cooks dream. The downstairs and upstairs bathrooms and laundry room has upgraded ceramic tile, additional canned lighting throughout the home and the great room and bonus room are prewired for surround sound speakers. Upstairs you'll find even more upgrades that will make this beautiful home even more attractive. The oversized master bedroom with double entry doors and sitting area is an owners dream. The master bathroom and secondary bathroom both have upgraded white cabinets and beautiful counters to match. Off of the master bathroom is your oversized walk in closet that has, more than enough room for the both of you. The extra wide hallway leads you past three amazing bedrooms and into a large bonus room that is large enough to accommodate all activities. Homestead Park is only a couple steps away where you will find a community pool, playground, dog park and BBQ area. If you are looking for a model condition and move in ready home then look no more! Contact me today for your VIP showing or virtual tour.

column10: If an office is desired - this home has it. This 20' x 17' downstairs flex room with full bathroom can also be used as an in-law quarters for multi-generational families, fitness room or quilting/craft room or a fifth bedroom. Double doors leading to the outside - so many options! Smoke free home priced below certified appraised value. Entering this beautiful home you step into a spacious foyer with high ceilings, 18'' porcelain tile throughout the first floor, warm colors, beautiful lighting and ceiling fans. Study/Den/Bedroom with large windows with a viewing of beautiful of plants and color. Off of this room is full bath/walk-in shower (wheelchair accessible). Beyond the foyer is an open view bending staircase to the second floor. There are many rooms in this home for enjoyment. The kitchen features maple wood cabinets with a rich cherry stain, granite countertops with grey, cherry and cream color compliments the cherry stained cabinets. Stainless steel appliances, 6-burner natural gas cooktop (also wired for electric). Built in convection and microwave. Center island can seat eight people (6' x 3.5') Adjoining the kitchen is breakfast nook which also adjoins the Family Room with large windows to the east and two fixed windows north side for lighting. Heatilator vent less gas fireplace with marble finish. Laundry room off kitchen features additional cherry colored cabinetry and cabinet sink. Off Laundry room 20'x17' Bedrm/Workout/Man Cave with full bath. Air conditioned two car garage with 10'x8'8 separated storage room. Master bedroom located on 2nd floor features walk-in shower, Jacuzzi tub, two vanities, large walk-in closet. Spacious guest bath features two separate vanities and large shower. Theater room (bonus room) is 20' x 20' and is wired for projection for a pull-down screen with surround sound. Off theater room is a 6' 1/2 x 22' storage room. Two additional bedrooms are located on the second floor. Northside bedroom 15'6 1/2''x13'4 , East bedroom 22'8 x13'4 (attached separate sitting rm/walk-in closet). Yard beautifully landscaped with a variety of mature plants and trees. Concreted walkway encompasses around the home. Privacy wood fence with multiple gates. Quiet Source generator-Completely services all electrical components

column10: Sophisticated design! This home is only 9 YEARS OLD! The design & floor plan of this home boasts the latest 'GREAT ROOM'' flow that today's new construction is offering. The extended Modern Picture Window style screen enclosure on patio is adorned by exquisite pavers & Japanese gardens on either side that overlook spectacular long lake views. Modern appointments include NEW A/C, volume ceilings, modern crown molding, neutral tile flooring and light and neutral paint colors. The open kitchen features a showcase window for extra natural lighting, high end cabinetry with undermount lighting granite counters, stainless steel appliances and a seated bar. The den boasts custom designer sliding doors with stainless steel accents that are shown in all the latest model homes. Owner's suite feature Owner's suite features custom outfitted walk-in closets, bath with upgraded cabinetry, separate his and hers vanities, water closet, and walk-in shower with bench seating. This home is all set with a custom frameless guest bath shower, designer lighting, custom blinds, Hunter Douglas window treatments, outfitted closets, a phantom screen at the front door, epoxy flooring and pull down attic stairs in garage, accordion shutters all around, and a new A/C!The Community has a newly renovated Clubhouse with resort style pool, wading pool, spa, cabanas, fitness center, aerobics studio and championship tennis center. Arts & Crafts room, Banquet room, billiards, catering kitchen.Enjoy the amenities that Four Seasons has to offer. Strong tennis program with 6 har-tru tennis courts, tennis pro and leagues for both men and women. Magnificent state of the art fitness center and a clubhouse with resort style pool, catering kitchen, card rooms and multi-purpose room. A Social Director is also onsite to plan great activities including parties, entertainment and more. Close to State Rd 7 and two major airports (Palm Beach International and Fort Lauderdale Hollywood Airports), major highways (Interstate 95 and Florida Turnpike) and highly rated medical facilities.

column10: Welcome to this immaculate 5 bed / 4 bath pool home located in the sought after neighborhood of Daniels Landing. This lakefront Eagle Harbor community is adored by many. Upon entry to this beautiful home, you are greeted by tall ceilings and views of the beautiful backyard pool area and landscaping through the french doors. This home comes with a formal dining area, an eat in area with a view, and an additional office space. The kitchen offers a walk in pantry, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a gas stove! The master bedroom includes tray ceilings, his and hers closets, access to the patio, and an ensuite bath! The ensuite bath has a garden tub with an additional walk in shower and two separate vanities! The backyard has a beautiful pool space complete with a waterfall and additional patio seating. You can enjoy the beautiful pool through the extended swimming season as the pool is heated by a solar heat system that also helps keep heating costs down for the pool. This house is directly near the neighborhood dock access as well!

column10: Look no further...country meets comfort with this pristine 5 bedroom 3 bath pool home on over an 1.3 acre landscaped lot on one of the most desired paved roads in sought average Loxahatchee. As you enter the beautiful cut glass entry double doors to the formal living and dining rooms your eyes can't help but go straight back to the waterfall feature of the pool. The over sized screened patio designed for a summer kitchen provides a wonderful extension for entertainment or gatherings with a 16 x 32 heated saltwater game pool & spa, with both solar and gas heater. Step outside the patio to a fenced in backyard including a fire pit area for those chilly nights where you want to sit back, relax and enjoy a bonfire. This meticulous home offers a 3-way bedroom split plan with... the Master Bedroom and one bedroom/den on one side of the house, 2 additional bedrooms and a bath off the kitchen and 5th bedroom and cabana bath off the family room. The kitchen is truly the heart of the home in this large open space including 42 in solid oak cabinetry with raised panel doors & granite counters, Stainless steel appliances, bar height counters for bar stools and breakfast area all overlooking your spacious family room. So many features to this property including an extended concrete driveway & front entry path, 6 zone sprinkler system with rain sensor on well, separate well for the house, double insulated attic, attic stairs & flooring, gutters, hurricane panels with all new hardware, & security flood lights at each corner. Additional interior features include knockdown walls, architectural planter shelves/cutouts, crown molding & chair rail detailing, arched doorways & rounded wall corners. Also includes a reverse osmosis sink and whole house water softener system & 2013 5 ton-17 seer Carrier A/C with a 10 year warranty, interior laundry room with front load washer & dryer and utility sink. Look no further...you found your home!

column10: Welcome home to LOW MAINTENANCE 17227 Old Tobacco Road. One of the largest 3 bedrooms in the entire community, your new home boasts 2, 300 SqFt and includes a huge BONUS room! Located in ultra desirable Lutz, you're minutes from both the Veterans Expressway and Dale Mabry and a short drive to both the airport and downtown Tampa! The 2016 newer built townhome sits on one of the BEST LOTS in the entire community, with no front or rear facing immediate neighbors and is loaded with tons of UPGRADES for you to enjoy! With LOW HOA fees, this gated community is a bit tucked away from the main road, making it the perfect retreat! Walking in you'll immediately notice your high ceilings, designer lighting fixtures and on trend feature pallet walls. Meal prep is easy in the spacious chefs kitchen with granite counters, oversized cabinetry and plenty of counter space. For additional storage/workspace, there is a custom built dry bar with wine fridge next to the closet pantry...the perfect spot for your coffee/smoothie station, wine fridge, juice boxes etc. Moving upstairs you'll find your oversized bonus area! Ideal for a second living room, work from home/virtual learning area or home gym-speaking of virtual learning...be sure to check out the incredible 'A' RATED SCHOOLS this home is zoned for!! Off of the bonus space is your tranquil owner suite with huge private bathroom and large walk-in closet. The split bedroom plan offers two additional spacious bedrooms overlooking the conservation area, full bath and laundry room upstairs. Storage will never be an issue as the sellers have taken extra care to add additional custom built-ins in multiple closets as well as the garage! The additional space is what you've been looking for, make 17227 Old Tobacco Road to your new home for 2021.

column10: Spectacular water views of Estero Bay, Gulf, Big Carlos Pass & Black Island. Rarely available. Welcome to this beautiful gated entry community with a stunning foyer & convenience of 2 elevators. This 2 bedroom + den Condo offers spacious open living area, oversized screened lanai w/electric storm shutters and breathtaking water views. Entrances to lanai from Great Room & Master Bedroom. Condo is freshly painted with 5 1/2 baseboards & beach washed floors add to coastal feel. Split bedrooms allow more beautiful water views & privacy. Laundry Room in residence with full washer, dryer & utility sink. Both bathrooms are spacious with dual sinks. Amenities include a 40' pool & spa, Fitness Room, Community Room, Pool Table, Library, BBQ area, outdoor shower, 2 private beaches, bayside sun deck, tennis and pickleball. Secured detached Parking Garage with designated space on 2nd level. Climate controlled large storage area for each condo & add'l storage area for Toys under Garage ramp. 10 boat docks some available to lease. Great Location next door to Lover's Key State Park, Flipper's on the Bay Restaurant and so much more. Embrace sunrise and sunset in your style here!

column10: Expect to be impressed as you step inside this architecturally distinct home located in Magnolia Point Golf & Country Club. It is the Palmetto floor plan by Drees, all on one level and beautifully upgraded. Tiled floors in the foyer continue throughout the main living areas with carpet only in the bedrooms. Entertaining options include formal dining, open living to kitchen and family rooms. A 3-way split for bedrooms offers privacy and a large owner's suite provides a luxurious bath with soaking tub, walk-in shower, double vanities and a huge closet. Enjoy evening breezes on the screened lanai with a view of the lagoon. There's a flex room that makes a perfect office. Laundry room has built-ins great for storage. The garage has special storage features.

column10: Perfect 2 bedroom plus den first floor end unit condo located in desired Villa Serena! Calming and private wooded view from your screened porch! Great South Brandon/Riverview location! Close to I-75, Winthrop Town Center's new restaurants, Super Target, and Home Depot. Single story downstairs units are hard to find - don't hesitate to make your appointment!!!

column10: Price Improvement!!!!! Don't miss out on the opportunity to own a beautifully-modernized home that sits on a lot with a massive kitchen and plenty of entertaining upgrades in the acclaimed Windsor community of Meadow Pointe. Not only does this home sit on a nice pond and conservation lot, it features the most scenic views with no homes to the back and on one side of it which equates to plenty of privacy. There are endless possibilities for the set up of your outside living area and for hosting events both inside and outside of the home. The brick paved and screened lanai features a custom wooden pergola with lanterns on all four columns to set the perfect ambiance in the evening. But wait until you enter the home! Upon entrance, from the foyer, you are taken aback by the sleek appearance of the home and the massive 14 feet kitchen quartz countertop island. Look down at where you're standing and you will notice the luxurious Junckers real hardwood flooring throughout the entire home with the exception of the bathrooms and laundry room. The kitchen was completely renovated in 2018 which now features 42 inch cabinets, luxury brand BOSCH kitchen appliances, white quartz countertops with gray veins, black undermount single basin granite composite kitchen sink with Kohler sensate touchless faucet with pull-down spout, plentiful cabinet storage on both sides of the 14ft kitchen island, and metallic stone backsplash. Where else can you find a kitchen this inviting and accommodating for 12+ people to gather for breakfast/lunch/dinner? As you bypass the kitchen and continue to tour the home, you are again greeted with the beautiful views through all the sliding doors and windows that allow for natural lighting. This home has 4 bedrooms with a den that can be used as an office. The laundry room features a barn door entrance, Samsung appliances, upper cabinets and a utility sink. All bathrooms have granite countertops, but wait until you see the chandelier above the garden tub which is framed by two columns in the master bathroom. The master bathroom features double sink vanity, separate large shower, and a wet room. In the master bedroom you'll find 2 walk in closets and a sitting area near the windows so that you can bask in the beautiful sunset views in the evening from the comforts of your bedroom. Should the new owner decide to add a pool, don't worry, this home already has a pool bath with a separate door outside of one of the secondary bedrooms. Don't waste another minute, schedule your appointment today to come tour your future home before it's snatched off of the market!!!

column10: Spectacular Standard Pacific (Somerset Model) 3,245 Sqft. home with 4 bedroom, 3.5 bathroom, 2 car garage located in the village of Sienna,  within the prestigious community of Estancia in Wesley Chapel. OVER 150k IN UPGRADES & OPTIONS!  You'll enjoy the Cul-De-Sac living along with the wonderful view of the pond and conservation from your covered Lanai and extended 18' X 16' brick paved open patio. Home boasts a bungalow style front porch, fully wood case windows throughout home, wood-look tile throughout the first level, beautiful coffered ceiling in the Master Bedroom and office/study, an enormous gourmet kitchen with upgraded stainless steel appliances including a sub-zero refrigerator, double wall oven, gas stove, microwave, dishwasher, a huge Island with an upgraded country style sink, disposal, breakfast bar, upgraded glass door cabinets with lighting, 42 inch wood cabinets, glass tile backsplash, a huge walk-in pantry with wood shelving, plenty of counter space, eat-in kitchen area and recess lighting. The Game Room area, located on the first level, can provide lots of entertainment, and it's huge double slider doors along with the many windows provides a great amount of natural light. The kitchen, Great Room, and Game Room provide an open concept which is great for entertaining family and friends. The second floor contains 4 bedrooms which includes a spacious bedroom with ensuite bath and a huge Master Suite. The Master Bath includes dual stainless steel sinks, upgraded faucets, a huge walk-in shower with large waterfall and an elongated garden tub. The walk-in Master Closet consists of custom built dresser, drawers, and shelving. Other features include a mudroom, laundry room with built-in cabinets and sink, On Demand Tankless hot water heater, water softener and much more! Estancia homeowners enjoy fabulous amenities including the fitness center and resort style pool. There are also walking trails, basketball courts, tennis courts, and a dog park. Home is convenient to schools, shopping, dining, malls, Hospital, major roadways and highways.

column10: Welcome to Westwood Estates, a beautiful equestrian friendly, gated community in Wesley Chapel. This stunning updated estate is nestled on just over an acre. Enjoy a pristine saltwater pool home with 5 bedrooms, plus bonus room/6th bedroom, 4 and 1/2 baths, and 3 car garage. The community is next to 7, 000 acres of preserve land, but just minutes from fantastic shopping including The Grove at Wesley Chapel, Shops at Wiregrass, Costco, Tampa Premium Outlets, Aldi, Publix, and wonderful dining options. Enjoy the natural light radiating through large windows and soaring ceilings throughout the home. The first floor exudes grandeur with a split floor plan, luxury vinyl plank flooring, an updated kitchen, granite counters, stainless-steel appliances, and french doors leading out to the pool. The master suite features large bay windows and direct access to the pool. Enjoy the spacious and updated master bathroom including his and hers walk-in closets, dual vanities, a large walk-in shower and a jetted tub by the bay window. The first floor includes a pool bathroom accessible from the pool deck. There is also a second bedroom on the first floor with a large walk in closet and full bathroom. Upstairs you will find an additional 3 bedrooms each with walk in closets, 2 full baths, and a massive bonus/game room that could be used as a 6th bedroom as there is a large walk in closet. The expansive backyard is fully enclosed with newer privacy fencing, has a garden area, as well as unique varieties of beautiful citrus and hibiscus trees. The lanai and 10, 000-gallon saltwater pool/spa are fully screened, all screen replaced in 2018. Low HOA fees of $600 a year, no CDD fees, RV/boat parking allowed, and the side fence features a large double gate for easy access. There is a multi-zone sprinkler system installed for front and back yards as well as a water softener for the home. The home has new blinds throughout, a new lift pump on the septic, fresh paint, newly updated kitchen and bathrooms, new chlorine generation system for the pool, new flooring on the first level, and much more. Schedule your showing today!

column10: Picture perfect and move-in-ready! Fabulous one-story maintenance-free home located in the highly sought after golf course community of Lexington Oaks in the gated Village of Pimlico. This (3-bedroom or 2-bedroom ) + office, 2-bathrooms, 2-car garage home is situated on a private and serene pond on a conservation lot with peaceful views of nature. This very popular floor plan offers 3-bedroom plan, however the sellers when building the home choose to use the 3rd bedroom/Den option as a den/living room, as offered by the builder, should the new buyer prefer the 3rd bedroom option, the buyer can choose to add a closet, (floor plan is available). Great room, open concept, which is open to the up-dated kitchen, with vaulted ceilings throughout. You will find casual dining space in the kitchen, which was remodeled in 2017. Sliders from the family room lead to the screened and partially covered extended lanai with peaceful views of the conservation and pond. The formal dining area is conveniently located adjacent to the kitchen. Per the seller the following was remodeled in 2017, all kitchen cabinets, all stainless appliances, granite counters with breakfast bar, decorative pendant lighting, built-in wall convection oven, wall microwave oven, glass top range with stainless hood and stainless-steel side by side refrigerator with beautifully tiled backsplash. Also remodeled in 2017, all of the lighting fixtures are dazzling and add a touch of style. Palm style ceiling fan in master bedroom, dual sinks with vanity and shower in master bath with vaulted ceilings throughout. Per the seller, new roofs are currently being installed by the association and is part of the HOA, and is in the process of changing all the roofs in Pimlico. The air conditioner was replaced in 2017, water conditioner in 2017 and all wood laminate flooring throughout in 2018 except for the bathrooms. Also included: Automatic garage door with security pad, garage attic ladder, and attic floor for storage as well as Storm shutters. All window treatment were also undated in 2017 on back sliding door leading to the lanai, venetian blinds and double paned window in master bedroom were replaced in 2017. Extended screened lanai for your enjoyment. Complete list of upgrades from seller can be found as an attachment. Located in the heart of Wesley Chapel, Lexington Oaks features an 18-hole golf course, club house, playground, a day care center, basketball courts, soccer fields, fitness center, and a community pool. The neighborhood is located near I-75, The Grove, Premium Outlets, Shops at Wiregrass, Advent Health, PHSC, Center Ice and much more. P.s. the office/den/living room does not have a closet. Welcome home!

column10: This beautiful well maintained home is still owned by the original homeowners in the highly desired Valrico neighborhood of Lithia Ridge. All original windows have been replaced with double glass windows, and high quality hurricane rated impact glass windows, to include the sliding glass doors for an additional level of security. The roof was replaced in 2013 with an anti-leak rubber mat underlayment material under the decorative architectural shingles. The entire air conditioning system was also upgraded in 2013 with an American Standard 5 ton 16 SEER (seasonal energy efficiency ratio) system. The entire home has been renovated with elegant neutral color porcelain and ceramic tile floor. The kitchen was renovated with granite countertops, matching granite island, decorative stone backsplash, and a glass burner stove. The kitchen also features a built in desk, a large walk in pantry, and spacious wooden cabinets. All three bathrooms have been improved with new accessories, and the laundry and hallway bathroom have solar tubes for daytime bonus lighting. There is a large guest room with its own private full bathroom. This homes exterior was painted in 2016, and has healthy manicured Saint Augustine turf with curbed florida friendly landscaping and polyvinyl security and privacy fencing. There is a tile roofed-in lanai with a large spacious yard for a pool of your choice. The built in security system has sensors on every door and window in addition to motion and smoke detectors. Six inch deep rain gutters surround the entire house. A new hot water heater was installed in 2018 and garage has been freshly repainted This home is connected to county sewer system, NO septic tank! Pride of ownership is evident throughout this property. Lithia Ridge is a very well established and sought after neighborhood with beautiful oak trees that canopy many of the streets. At the entrance there is a large beautiful park with a lake, soccer field, beach volleyball and basketball courts, covered pavilion with picnic tables and a grill, and a large shaded playground. The A rated Lithia Springs Elementary School is in walking distance through the neighborhood park. Nearby Fishhawk Randall Middle School and Newsome High Schools are also rated schools. HOA fees are only $27 per month, and there are no CDD fees. This move in ready home is a must see in a great community!

column10: YOUR SEARCH ENDS HERE!! You don't want to miss this RARE OPPORTUNITY to own this ORIGINAL OWNER POOL HOME with some of the BEST AND MOST AMAZING POND & CONSERVATION VIEWS in Bloomingdale!! Located in the Somerset section of the highly sought-after Bloomingdale community, this home has everything you have been looking for. With quick easy access to shopping, restaurants, schools, gyms, sports & medical facilities this home features just under 3, 100 heated sq ft, 4 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, a huge bonus room, an 3 car oversized garage and offers a 3 way split bedroom floor plan that is very unique. What you are going to love about this house...1. Formal area with foyer, his and hers office, dining room, living room and entry to master bedroom. 2. Casual living area with large eat in nook, family room and huge kitchen with pantry, tons of counter space, lots of all wood cabinets and drawers & sponge tray in all for storage and includes upgraded stainless steel appliances. This area connects to bedroom 3 and pool bath. 3. The upstairs bonus room / man cave (with 3 tap kegerator) is complete with wet bar and is joined to a bonus room area first floor bathroom and bedrooms 1 & 2. This home features tons of storage including a front coat closet, rear linen closet as well as attic & under-staircase storage areas. All traffic and wet areas are tiled. The office and family room offer laminated floors. Outside the spacious lanai and kidney shaped pool with freshly painted pool deck and sturdy pebble-tec finish provide low maintenance for years to come. The real draw to this home is the back yard having 2 ponds and trails that lead to a private park for residents only. There are other trails that lead through conservation area to the Alafia River. There is a deck off the lanai with a perfect spot for a fire pit. This home is ideally located in a quiet area with no back-yard neighbors, a short distance to an A-rated elementary school, access to an over 10 acre private park for the community; ideal for dogs, and outdoor activities. YMCA, restaurants, shops, and pick-up/drop-off point for Mc Dill AFB shuttle are nearby.

column10: Much sought after 4 bedroom home with large rear yard. Great room floor plan with vaulted ceilings. Kitchen is located of the right with eat-in space. Utility closet in kitchen for washer and dryer. Nice sized master bedroom with full master bathroom. Large walk-in closet. Bedrooms #2 and #3 located at the front left of home with bathroom #2. Fourth bedroom located on back rear of home which also could be an office or play room. Two car attached garage. Located at the back of the subdivision on a dead end street which limits the traffic. This allows lots of space for kids to play and ride their bikes in the street. Low HOA fees. No CDD fees. No flood insurance. For you golfing enthusiasts, you are within 20 minutes of 10-12 different golf clubs including the famous Saddlebrook Golf Resort. All three local schools ( Watergrass Elementary School, Weightman Middle School and Wesley Chapel High School) are conveniently located within 5 minutes of home. Finally the main campus of the University of South Florida is just 15-20 away. Just 5 -10 minutes off interstate 75 which allows access to many other amenities such as Tampa Premium Outlets, The Shops at Wiregrass and the fast growing city of Wesley Chapel. Tons of stores, restaurants and more. 75 also gives access into downtown Tampa Bay and connection to Interstate 4 which will take you over to Orlando.

column10: This stunning 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom, 2 car garage Sea Breeze home built by Beazer Homes in 2019 is located on a beautiful conservation homesite with no rear neighbors. Located in the Avalon Park community in Wesley Chapel you will be able to enjoy the private conservation views from your lanai or from the many windows that allow natural light in the great room, dining room and master bedroom. This single-story home has an open concept floorplan perfect for entertaining. The front door and entry from the garage opens to a foyer/mud room, which boasts a tray ceiling, leads to the open concept living area. With the secondary bedrooms separate from the master bedroom creating privacy and reducing noise. The well appointed kitchen overlooks the great room and features 42 inch cabinets, granite countertops, large walk-in pantry with outlets added to allow for easy access to a second refrigerator if needed, and a large island with built-in Breakfast bar that's perfect for family gatherings. Massive great room with sliding doors that open on to a covered lanai for summer barbecues. Master bedroom features an attached en-suite with two walk-in closets, a large walk-in shower, and dual vanity with granite countertops. Avalon Park West includes amazing family-friendly amenities like a fitness pool, a resort-style zero entry pool, spa, splash park, playgrounds, clubhouses, grilling and pinic areas, walking trails, dog park, and more!!

column10: Super neat and tidy three bedroom two bath home situated on a corner lot in Silver Oaks. Silver Oaks is one of Zephyrhills finest communities. It offers an 18-hole championship golf course with clubhouse, restaurant, pro-shop, driving range and event center. You can join the Club and use your own golf cart on the course. Silver Oaks streets are private so you can use your golf cart on them. Across the street is the East Pasco YMCA with olympic size pool, basketball courts and gym. The Sara Vande Berg Tennis & Wellness Center is located just across Simons Road from Silver Oaks. 1/2 mile from the back automatic gate at Silver Oaks is a movie theater, bowling alley, restaurants, major big box stores and grocery stores. Silver Oaks Has over 5 miles of sidewalks to use. The home was custom built by Bill Poe Construction. You enter through the front door into a large living room with beautiful big picture window. The dining room is light and bright with 3 windows and sliders leading to the screened covered lanai. The kitchen has plenty of cabinet space and is open to the dining room. There is an indoor utility room, automatic irrigation system and single car garage.

column10: Truly a move-in ready, spacious 2295sf condo with an attached 2 car garage! The lanai of this end unit, overlooks a calming pond with plenty of wildlife to watch while having a morning cup of coffee! Located within the Preserve at Lansbrook, this home features a very open floor plan, volume ceilings, 2 bedrooms, 2 baths and a 20x18 bonus room with endless possibilities i.e. media room or rec room. Super-size kitchen with eat-in area, prep island and walk-in pantry. A spacious master bath with separate tub and step in shower, double vanities and walk in closet. Upgraded features include engineered wood floors, brand new Samsung stainless kitchen appliances, new upgraded granite kitchen counter tops and bathroom vanity counter tops, & new water softener. A large inside laundry room with super large storage closet. This is a 2nd level condo with a private entry staircase and attached garage. The Preserve at Lansbrook has its own private heated salt water community pool and only a short walk to the Lansbrook Community Park situated on the shores of Lake Tarpon, with boat ramp, docks, playgrounds and picnic areas. Enjoy a maintenance free lifestyle with low monthly fees. Please view the virtual tours and matterport walk-through and floor plan!

column10: Welcome to 424 Buckhead Ct. This beautiful cul-de-sac home is nestled in the established community of Durbin Crossing. With fabulous community amenities from a luxury pool with a slide to a large playground. There is plenty of activities for the whole family. The first floor includes a formal dining room, formal living room, bedroom that can be an office, full bathroom, family room and eat in kitchen. The kitchen features gorgeous white cabinets, a vibrant backsplash and granite countertops. The open kitchen has new stainless-steel appliances, breakfast bar, food prep island and an eat in space. The bedroom/office has French doors and a closet. Heading upstairs, you a greeted with a large loft perfect for family game nights or a playroom. The large master suite has walk-in closets, a lovely master bathroom. Featuring a garden tub, stand up shower and dual sinks. 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms and a laundry room compete the upstairs. New carpets and wood flooring. This home has 40K worth of upgrades! The backyard is an outdoor lover's paradise. On hot summer days you can relax in the fabulous screened in pool. The homes orientation allows for the perfect summer breeze. The oversized lot gives you plenty of space and the already established garden beds and mature fruit tress (peach, avocado, navel orange, blood orange, Meyer lemon, lime and a strawberry patch) are perfect for growing your own produce. Call us today for your private tour!

column10: This stunning three story townhome is located in The Reserve at Sea Forest, a gated community with HOA association providing maintenance free living. This Mediterranean style 3 bedroom, 3 bath, 2 car garage townhome boasts 2, 122 SqFt. From the garage to each level of the home has the luxury style expected by most demanding buyers. On the 2nd level you will find an open floor plan with the kitchen, living room-dining room combo. The gourmet kitchen features solid wood cabinetry with convective oven, microwave, gas cook top, granite counter tops and a huge breakfast bar perfect for entertaining all of your friends and family. The living room features a gas fireplace and sliding doors opening up to the balcony. On the 3rd level double doors open wide to a massive master bedroom with amazing water views, and a charming gas fireplace. The master bedroom also boasts its own private balcony where you can take in breathtaking sunset views looking out over the Gulf. The spa like mater bathroom features a large dual sink vanity with granite countertop, relaxing jetted tub, and a separate stand up shower. You will appreciate the inside laundry room with mud sink, and all the extra storage throughout the home. HOA membership to the Gulf Landings Association gives you access to their swimming pool, Jacuzzi, tennis court, boat ramp and clubhouse and the membership to Gulf Harbors Beach Club let you enjoy their rare private beach. Schedule a private showing today. You won't want to miss out on this one!

column10: BACK ON MARKET!!!Picture Perfect Condominium in Regency Palms is located just minutes away from the vibrant downtown area of New Port Richey that has a number of local restaurants and social spots. As an owner in Regency Palms you are afforded optional membership to the private beach located in Gulf Harbors for only $156 per year. This 3 bedroom/2 bathroom condo has just about everything, but a new owner. The sellers spared no expense and added numerous features as the original owners of this unit, built in 2014. The list of upgrades can be made available upon request. The building has 3 levels, the ground floor consists of garages and storage rooms and the next 2 floors are condos. The real plus of being on the top floor is that the unit has 10ft vaulted ceilings giving it a very open and airy feel. The kitchen is stunning with an extended island for plenty of prep space for those who love to cook. The counters are granite and rich wood cabinet have crown molding at the top and bottom of the upper cabinets. The lower cabinets have pullout drawers. Both bathrooms have the same countertops and cabinets as the kitchen offering elegance throughout the condo. The layout is very open and great for entertaining. As you enter you have the dining area just off the kitchen which looks out to the spacious living room that leads out to the balcony overlooking a nice size retention pond and community pool. There are split bedrooms with the Master Suite near the front door and the other 2 bedrooms and guest bath at the rear of the condo. There is tile throughout and the downstairs storage room which is 21' by 10.5' and would make a great exercise or music studio, is carpeted and is opposite the 1 car garage. Regency Palms has a community pool, heated spa with a BBQ area. Put this one on your list to see today as you will not be disappointed!

column10: Welcome to this beautiful 3 bedroom plus an office, 3 full bath 2 car energy efficient home in the desireable community of Meadow Pointe in the Heart of Wesley Chapel. Built in 2017, and meticulously maintained, you will enjoy the spectacular 1 floor layout. You can not beat the large lot backing to a pond and conservation area. NO REAR NEIGHBORS! Before you even enter the home, enjoy the upscale landscaping with night time lighting. The seller upgraded all the flooring to custom wood look tile floors throughout, NO Carpeting! Blinds throughout the home convey to the new owners. The sellers has installed storage shelving in the garage and will also convey with the home. The entire home is pre-wired throughout and part of the smart home package. Security system and ring doorbell also installed. Everyone will enjoy the quiet, gated community and its features. But first enjoy the spacious, beautiful open kitchen with HUGE Quartz Island open to the large family room. There is also a walk in pantry for all your kitchen storage needs. The kitchen has built in microwave and oven. Prep work is easy with the large country sink. Cooking is a pleasure on the flat top range with decorative hood vent and backsplash. This is the heart of the home and you can enjoy family and friend gatherings. The master suite is away from the other bedrooms in this split plan layout. There is a large shower and stand alone tub. Every bedroom has it's own bathroom and large closets. Enjoy the back yard view and nature in the screened lanai or enjoy one of Tampa's Championship teams on the Lanai TV. Meadow Pointe IV has access to a beautiful community pool, tennis and basketball courts, If schools are a concern Meadow Pointe is surrounded by top rated schools. Close to Tampa, shopping, restaurants, outlet malls and every amenity you can think of. Enjoy the very LOW HOA dues and No flood insurance required in this X zone lot and ready for new homeowners.

The 2 car garage includes a 67 gallon GeoSprint energy efficient hot water heater. You will also love the upgrades that include a water filter and water softener, washer and dryer off the kitchen and a oversized pantry with additional storage and unique shelving. AC unit is a 3 ton energy efficient heat pump with extra storage in the air handler closet, which is located on the second floor closet.

column2: 7219 Meeting House Ln, Apollo Beach, FL, 33572
column10: Look no further you dream home is here! This beautiful 4 bedroom home has all the upgrades, being a former model home, it comes loaded with accents you only see in photos. Located in front of the lake you have no neighbors across the street and you can enjoy sunset views from your bedroom window. Not a thing was missed in this home, from a pavered driveway and the beautiful stone accents on the front of the home you will be impressed from the start. Enter through your leaded glass front door to the soaring ceiling in an inviting entryway. The huge open concept kitchen, dining, and living space is a perfect floorplan for entertaining with in ceiling surround sound and is trimmed with 5 1/2 in baseboards and crown molding. In the gorgeous gourmet kitchen you have a huge oversized island, beautiful glazed cream wood cabinets with added glass fronts, quartz countertops, a 5 burner gas stove, a glass door walk in pantry, glass subway tile backsplash, and Kitchen Aid stainless steel appliances. The main floor of the home has brand new ceramic tile flooring throughout. Your visiting family & friends can enjoy a private downstairs bedroom and bath. Upstairs you will find an oversized master suite with a beautifully accented ceiling tray, dual sinks, and a glass tiled shower in the en-suite bath plus a huge walk in closet. The 2 remaining bedrooms share a jack and jill bathroom with private vanities on each side and their own walk-in closets. Back downstairs there is plenty of natural light from 2 sets of sliding glass doors that open up to extend your living space outside to the extra large, paved and screened lanai. The pavers continue out for a great entertaining space around the lush landscaping and gas firepit to enjoy on chilly evenings. The home also includes an in-wall pest control system. Located in the family friendly community of Waterset this home is positioned directly between all three of the best entertainment spaces, to the north you have the clubhouse that includes a restaurant, fitness center, community pool, and fishing dock. Just a short walk from your driveway takes you to the giant splash pad for the littles and a dog park for your furry friends. To the south is another resort style pool with waterslides. This community has all the activities you could need from food truck rally nights, concerts at the amphitheater, turkey trots and much much more! Please note there is no homestead exemption on this years taxes so when you make this your primary home you will gain the Florida Homestead tax deduction, reducing taxes! THIS IS THE ONE you won't want to miss!

The pavers continue out for a great entertaining space around the lush landscaping and gas firepit to enjoy on chilly evenings. The home also includes an in-wall pest control system. Located in the family friendly community of Waterset this home is positioned directly between all three of the best entertainment spaces, to the north you have the clubhouse that includes a restaurant, fitness center, community pool, and fishing dock. Just a short walk from your driveway takes you to the giant splash pad for the littles and a dog park for your furry friends. To the south is another resort style pool with waterslides. This community has all the activities you could need from food truck rally nights, concerts at the amphitheater, turkey trots and much much more! Please note there is no homestead exemption on this years taxes so when you make this your primary home you will gain the Florida Homestead tax deduction, reducing taxes! column10: "Lowest HOA fee in the Tampa Bay Area. Enjoy this beautiful and impeccably kept townhome located in the quiet and convenient community of Sawgrass Village. The spacious master is en suite and has a soaking tub, separate shower and a walk in closet. The large gourmet kitchen has all new stainless steel appliances, a long breakfast bar and custom tile backsplash. The laundry room is located upstairs and has a new washer and dryer. The garage has enclosed overhead storage, a new epoxy floor, and new garage door opener complete with Wi-Fi. There is a new nest thermostat and ring video doorbell. The water heater is new and there is a water softener. All of the lights are LED. There are occupancy light sensors in the bathrooms, laundry room and walk in closet. Sawgrass village is conveniently located just 25 minutes from Tampa, 15 minutes from Downtown St. Pete, 20 minutes from the beach and 21 minutes from Tampa International Airport. column10: Welcome Home! This light and bright Smith Farm pool home has much to offer! Situated on an oversized, fenced lot that backs up to a private preserve, this home features fresh, neutral paint, wood floors through-out the first level, a large living space and an interior laundry room. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances, and an adjacent dining room that leads out to the rear screened patio. You'll enjoy living the Florida lifestyle to its fullest with the open, sparkling swimming pool, which includes a baby gate and waterfall, plus a backyard with plenty of room to play. Additional features include newer carpet and ceiling fans in the bedrooms, generous closet space, newer privacy and sun-blocking blinds, a Nest thermostat system, new garage door and accordion storm shutters. Smith Farm is a 24/7 Guard gated community that offers its residents amenities including a fitness room, 2 resort like pool areas, a tot lot, splash pad and soccer, softball fields, tennis and basketball courts and more! Zoned for desirable ''A'' rated Coral Reef Elementary and Park Vista High and only a short drive to shopping, dining and more. Fiber optic Xfinity cable and high speed internet are included in your affordable monthly HOA fee!

column10: Located in the desirable Rock Springs Ridge community, this beautiful 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom is an amazing home that can make memories for years to come. With a split floor plan this home offers a front formal living room/office/den across from a separate formal dining room. The kitchen opens up to the family room with glass doors looking out to the screened-in patio/pool area which helps bring in beautiful natural light. The master bedroom also offers a glass slider to the pool/patio area, a walk-in closet with built-ins with an attached master bathroom with a separate shower, jacuzzi tub and double sink areas. The 2nd and 3rd bedrooms have a bathroom in between while the 4th bedroom is located in the back next to the 3rd bathroom with a door leading to the pool area. The kitchen has a walk in pantry with shelving, a BRAND NEW gas stove and stainless steel sink. Laundry room is it's own room with Maytag front loader washer and dryer. Solar panels for heating the pool, the house is also wired with for a security system as well as 4 cameras with a monitor for viewing. Conveniently located near the Northwest Complex which has football, baseball, soccer, softball fields, tennis courts, basketball courts, sand volleyball, a beautiful lake with a sidewalk around it as well as a covered Amphitheater where different events are held throughout the year! Highway 429 is within 3 miles, and Mount Dora is a quick commute away with shopping and restaurants nearby. Both the Elementary and Middle schools are on the bus route, but within walking/bike riding distance. This home is ready for a new family with great memories. Schedule your appointment today.

column10: Are you looking for elegance, quality and room to roam? This well maintained, move in ready home located on a cul de sac will please the most discerning buyer. Main home is 2570 square feet with 4 bedrooms and potential for 5th bedroom, 3 bathrooms, large kitchen, walk in pantry, one of those 4 bedrooms could be a guest suite or second owners suite, open floor plan, indoor laundry, electric fireplace, tile and wood floors through out. The home has too many features to list here, you must see. The detached apartment is 625 square feet with 1 bedroom, 1 bath, a large walk in shower, laundry area, sun deck, fenced and a beautiful upgraded kitchen with stainless appliances, solid counters, soft close cabinetry and mini split HVAC system. Apartment completely remodeled 3 years ago. The detached 3 car garage/workshop has 2 large bay doors and a walk in door, plus on each exterior side are attached metal carports and in back there is a large attached metal carport used as a lien too for parking mowers. Property has large 12 x 20 metal storage building with lots of windows allowing building to be used for multiple things such as a garden house, work shop, studio, storage, etc.Main house, apartment and detached garage are concrete block construction filled with concrete and brick accent built sturdy to withstand Florida's hurricane weather. So Build also includes foam board insulation between exterior walls and drywall, and vinyl 2-tone low E windows throughout home and apartment. Both home and apartment have solid wood cabinetry and granite counters. Main home HVAC has 4 micro filter and both delivery and return have metal ducts. Apartment has a new mini split HVAC system. All main wiring is in conduit to allow ease of expansion or work. Generac Station that runs home, apartment and workshop. 2 propane tanks, 2 septics (one for main home, one for apartment). Truly this home is well constructed and designed. Schedule your showing today, this is a must see home!
